      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ZELDA COVILHA (1) looks close to another win after finishing third from Box 2 last time (29.51) at Sandown. Likely to be in the finish again. NARADHAN (8) has a strong record this trip with five wins and three placings from 10 starts. Was out of placings last time (30.09) at Sandown in a Grade 5, finishing fifth and beaten 9 lengths. Looks suited here and can measure up. OVER ACHIEVER (2) turned in a better run last time to find a minor placing (28.08) at this track behind Hoppy in a Grade 4/5. Led around the bend before fighting on well and should give a sight. Ran one of the fastest times on the program last start despite finishing in the minors. Can measure up. UNCLE STILTSKIN (4) recorded a one length win (29.65) in a Grade 5 last time at Sandown. Has already won two times from this draw.",
